headline: 3 High-Yielding Dividend Stocks That Retirees Can Rely On for Recurring Income
summary: If you're a retiree and want some dependable income, high-yielding dividend stocks can help make the most of your money.  For retirees, three blue chip stocks that can be ideal options for your portfolio include Bristol Myers Squibb (NYSE: BMY), Enbridge (NYSE: ENB), and Coca-Cola (NYSE: KO).  Drugmaker Bristol Myers pays a dividend that yields 4.5% right now.
